Package: sacADos
Type: Package
Title: Discrete Optimisation for Feature Selection: the 0-1 Knapsack Problem in R and Rcpp
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-03
Author: Mahir Dursunoglu
Maintainer: Mahir Dursunoglu <mahir.dursunoglu@mindlapse.ai>
Description: Implementations of the 0-1 knapsack problem applied to feature
    selection under a resource budget. Provides a naive exhaustive search and a
    dynamic-programming solver in R and Rcpp, a branch-and-bound solver using a
    max-heap priority queue in Rcpp, and a fast heuristic (greedy construction
    plus k-exchange local search) with a computable LP optimality bound. Also
    provides instance generators for several weight/value distributions used to
    benchmark the algorithms.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
